  Military decorations
McPeak's military decorations include the:

  Defense Distinguished Service Medal
  Air Force Distinguished Service Medal
  Silver Star
  Legion of Merit (with oak leaf cluster)
  Distinguished Flying Cross (olc)
  Meritorious Service Medal
  Air Medal (13 olc)
  Air Force Commendation Medal (3 olc)
  Vietnam Service Medal (4 service stars)
  National Defense Service Medal
  Combat Readiness Medal
  Air Force Overseas Service Ribbon Long Tour
  Air Force Overseas Service Ribbon Short Tour
  Air Force Expert Marksmanship Ribbon
  Republic of Vietnam Gallantry Cross
  Vietnam Campaign Medal.

Qualification badges include the Command Aviator Badge, the Parachutist Badge, and the Office of the Joint Chiefs of Staff Identification Badge
