Branch Office Profile

The Merrill Lynch Oakland Office focuses on delivering wealth management strategies to high net worth individuals and businesses while delivering exemplary service. It is our goal to differentiate Merrill Lynch from other financial services companies and to educate the East Bay community on the value of disciplined saving and investing with a focus on personalized client service.   In an ever-changing financial world, an experienced advisor can make all the difference. Our Financial Advisors have guided clients through virtually every market condition and can help you stay disciplined, identify and capture opportunities, and have confidence in your investment strategy—even during periods of great volatility. With our combined years of service in the financial services industry, we can help you chart a course designed to achieve your goals. And as markets evolve, we can review and update it as needed.   Our primary focus is to go beyond financial strategies and help clients achieve the life they want.








